	<plot>Getafix the Druid is out of magic potion! If Caesar finds out, it's invasion for sure. Asterix and Obelix set out to find the necessary herbs. A mission through all sorts of Roman-infested terrain - seas and rivers, forests and deserts, temples and ruins.Cheat: Infinite LivesOn the first level, break the rocks and use the water spout to reach the cloud platforms. Go across to find an extra life, go back so where the extra life was is off the screen. Return back to where the extra life was and it will re-appear. Do this until you have 9 lives (the maximum). You can also do it on other levels.</plot>
